page.title: 20CREDITS
page.content: This project has been undertaken by two forms of{Ashdown House School.}The field work was done by Uju Asika, Lucy Bond, Lucinda and Sophie Bennet,Tom Clowes,Hugo Currie,Kate Comer, Alexander Demattio,Marlowe Fawcett,Zoe Foster, James Gerson, Michael Guyver, Swithin Long, Tristain McCowan, Barnaby Parker, Katrina Thompson,Sasha Unwin.Parts of the text have been written by Adam Nathan, Garath Lewis, Alastair Harrison, Nad Segram, Danish Shah, Matthew Hegarty, Adam Tomes, Stuart Robinson and Suvir Sakhrani. The photographs were taken by Mr. Duncan Hepburn.
